Full Description: Revelstone provides the only web-based platform that combines the power of performance analytics, benchmarking, and reporting to citizens in one solution.  Revelstone Compass helps municipalities of all sizes to make data-driven decisions based on facts, not politics or the status quo.  Compass drives new insights, operational efficiencies, better communication, and improved outcomes for citizens.  Revelstone was founded in 2010 by a small group of software and consulting executives with deep experience working with Fortune 500 companies in performance management.  They recognized that the tools and approaches available to help municipal managers were outdated, and insufficient to overcome the serious challenges facing their local governments to ‘do more with less.’  Inspired by the remarkable results big cities and businesses have had using good data to manage well within resource constraints, they designed Revelstone Compass specifically to bring these expensive capabilities to local governments in an affordable and easy-to-use format.  These goals were achieved by combining best-of-breed capabilities from enterprise software like IBM and Oracle with a cloud-based solution.  They believe that a fundamental transformation in the way cities think, operate, deliver services, and engage with their citizens is underway across America.  They are proud to have participated in the inaugural Code for America accelerator, and continue working with Code for America supporting much-needed data-driven innovations for their communities.

You can request anything you want, including experiences! All you have to do is choose a picture to represent the item you want using our image library or by uploading your own picture. After you choose the picture, you tell us how much you need to raise to get the item. All Things Wishful divides the image into a grid of clickable tiles based on the price you set. Tell your friends about your registry by sending them your unique All Things Wishful URL, and you're ready to start receiving. Your friends choose an item from your registry and use our clickable tiles to let us know which portions of the items they would like to buy you. We collect the funds from your friends and deposit them into your Amazon Payments account; you watch your balance grow. With your funds, you can get what you want, when you want and from where you want. You don't have to worry about shipping and handling charges, getting rid of packaging and returning gifts that you don't want.

Description: Asobi is a social and discovery platform for gamers of all skill levels to find, play, and socialize with each other.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Phoenix Area, Western US
Full Description: Despite the tremendous growth of the video game and esport industries, there is no universal platform for gamers of all backgrounds and skill set to find, socialize, and play with each other. As gaming becomes more "social" it becomes increasingly more difficult to find other people (outside of an immediate friend group) to play with and against each other.  Asobi is a discovery platform that allows gamers of all skill levels to find, socialize, and play with each other. We are the only platform that hosts a gaming database of over 100,000 games. Users can utilize the database to create their own gaming list. Their list consists of details which include the console they play their games on, their status on the game, and their top 5 favorite games. By applying these details in conjunction with Asobi's matching technology, users can easily search for others who share similar game interests. Asobi's searching tool includes functionality that allows users to search for other gamers’ profiles by their in-game names (with user consent). By providing a platform that allows gamers to find others and ultimately decrease anonymity, a clearer perspective of the wants and needs of gaming enthusiasts. This presents an advantage for organizations to better analyze their fans.
